        <p xml:id="auto_fyvk9s8d">
            <ol xml:id="auto_0pvw2qn6">
                <li xml:id="auto_j35t911r">
                    <p xml:id="auto_trqzfptx">
                        The figure below shows <m>AP,\,BQ, \textbf{and}\,CR</m> perpendicular to 
                        <m>OV \text{and } \, \angle \, TOV=\theta </m>
